author: The Current
description:
Mt. Joy felt inspired by the coyotes they saw roaming near Los Angeles
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

During an interview at The Current, Mt. Joy's Matt Quinn talks about feeling inspired to write the song "Coyotes" after observing the wild canines roaming Mount Washington in Los Angeles. "Coyotes" appears on Mt. Joy's album, "Hope We Have Fun."
